  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 2\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2 - 25 \u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "2 million people register for fuel license - valid all over the island from 25",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy, says that more than 2 million people have registered for the National Fuel License as of 4:00 pm today.",
        "The minister insisted that this system will be tested at several places in Colombo on the 21st and at the same time the system of issuing fuel according to the last digit of the vehicle number plate will also be implemented.",
        "Also, the minister further said that the national fuel license system will be implemented throughout the island from the 25th."
      ],
